dct_title_s: Marshrutnai︠a︡ turisticheskai︠a︡ skhema. Iz Kabardino-Balkarii v Svanetii︠u / Skhema Tbilisskoĭ kartograficheskoĭ fabrikoĭ GUGK v 1958 g. i ispravlena v 1960 g. ; Redaktor Akopova K. S. ; Konsul'tant Shli︠a︡pak A. E.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights and shading. Shows Soviet Republic borders, roads, railroads, waterfalls, gardens, tourist routes and sites, mineral water springs, glaciers. Insert: descriptions of landmarks and the city of Nalchik. Ancillary map: Konet͡s turistckogo marshruta iz Kabardino-Balkarii v Svanetii︠u (1:600 000). Ancillary map: Конец туристского маршрута из Кабардино-Балкарии в Сванетию (1:600 000). Verso: Notes for  tourists. Publisher's no.: E-325. Е-325.
dct_spatial_sm: Russia. Russian Empire. Soviet Union. Former Soviet Republics
